               <scopecontent id="aspace_fcd7950464455310e66f4a9a000d7e22">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Enclosing part of an opera (not present) and discussing an opera project</p>
               </scopecontent>
               <bioghist id="aspace_d2baf2d6390093d51d686a108dc992b3">
                  <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
                  <p>Colonna was the leading composer of sacred and secular dramas of the Bolognese school</p>
               </bioghist>
