               <scopecontent id="aspace_e4877d382037d9225020a92f11256363">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>About his Mass for two seven-part choirs, describing the accompaniment of four violins, and four wind instruments, violone and organ</p>
               </scopecontent>
               <bioghist id="aspace_ab90990df17ff52a54ef7e2e11a63a05">
                  <head>Biographical/Historical note</head>
                  <p>Goretti was Monteverdi's assistant during preparations for <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                        <part>Mercurio e Marte</part>
                     </title> in 1628</p>
                  <p>See A. Rosenthal, <title localtype="simple" render="italic">
                        <part>Obiter Scripta</part>
                     </title>, p. 202 and 208, where the letter is illustrated</p>
               </bioghist>
            </c>
